                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for synergistically preparing nitrogen fertilizer by using waste ammonium salt and ardealite to reduce pollution and carbon of biogas",
                    "一种废铵盐与磷石膏对沼气减污降碳协同制备氮肥的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for synergistically preparing a nitrogen fertilizer by using waste ammonium salt and ardealite to reduce pollution and carbon of biogas, which comprises the following steps: firstly, dissolving the waste ammonium salt, and separating the ammonium salt by using a struvite crystallization method; the struvite is dried at low temperature to generate ammonia gas, and ammonia water is prepared by adopting an absorption method; then, ammonia water and solid waste phosphogypsum (CaSO4) are fully mixed, carbon dioxide and hydrogen sulfide in the biogas are absorbed, and a building material calcium carbonate, a nitrogen fertilizer (NH4) 2SO4 and ammonium sulfide are formed. Calcium carbonate is separated and recycled through precipitation. Ammonium sulfide is aerated to form elemental sulfur, the elemental sulfur is separated from (NH4) 2SO4 precipitation, and nitrogen fertilizer and sulfur can be recycled. After CO2 and H2S in the biogas are captured, CH4 energy efficiency and cleanliness are greatly improved. The thought of treating waste with waste is adopted, the waste ammonium salt and the solid waste phosphogypsum are recycled, and pollution reduction and carbon reduction of the biogas are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种废铵盐与磷石膏对沼气减污降碳协同制备氮肥的方法，包括以下步骤，首先将废铵盐溶解，通过鸟粪石结晶法分离出铵盐；鸟粪石通过低温烘干生成氨气，采用吸收法制备成氨水；之后将氨水与固废磷石膏(CaSO4)充分混合，吸收沼气中的二氧化碳与硫化氢，形成建筑材料碳酸钙、氮肥(NH4)2SO4和硫化铵。碳酸钙通过沉淀分离回收。硫化铵经过曝气后形成硫单质，与(NH4)2SO4沉淀分离，可回收氮肥和硫磺。沼气中的CO2与H2S被捕集后，CH4能源效率和清洁度将大幅提升。本发明采取“以废治废”的思路，不仅废铵盐和固废磷石膏得到了资源化，还实现了沼气的减污降碳。"
                }
            ]
